Trade/Device Name(s): FORA Diamond Prima Blood Glucose Monitoring System
FORA Diamond Mini Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): FORA Diamond Prima Blood Glucose Meter
FORA Diamond Mini Blood Glucose Meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for FORA Diamond Prima and Mini Blood Glucose Monitoring Systems using electrochemical biosensor technology for home glucose monitoring in diabetic patients.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for self-testing of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from the finger by people with diabetes mellitus at home, to aid in monitoring diabetes control; not for diagnosis or screening, use on neonates, or sharing.
